cnn 具有三种基本层 卷积层(conv)、池化层(pool)、全连接层(FC)

conv layer

input : n_h * n_w * n_c
hyperparameters:  s :strides
                  f :filter size
                  p :padding
                  n_c_new :number of filter

parameters : w: f *f * n_c* n_c_new
             b: bias
output: n_h_new = int( (n_h+ 2*p - f )/s + 1)
        n_w_new = int( (n_w+ 2*p - f )/s + 1)
        n_c_new
优势:
    参数共享
    局部感知
    多核卷积

pool layer:
input : n_h * n_w * n_c
hyperparameters: f: filter size
                 s: strides

type : Max or average
output: n_h_new = int( (n_h - f )/s + 1)
        n_w_new = int( (n_w - f )/s + 1)
        n_h

pool layer 能提取出真正能识别特征的数值，丢弃不重要的数值

FC layer:
